 BTW, you cannot buy a used cat at any wrecking yard in Calif. Against the law
for them to sell them, so they whack them off when they have 'em up on the
rack draining all the fluids. Good luck finding a good cross-over pipe, they
usually whack off the cat at the U bend of the cross-over! And the muffler is
usually welded to the cat, so that is gone also.

